ps://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/real-floors-commercial/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/delta-faucet/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/pulleyassociates/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/schluter-systems/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/traditions-in-tile/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/cowan-supply/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/cr-construction-v2/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/cambria/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/top-knobs/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/tko-plumbing/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/servicewise-electric/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/american-signature-furniture/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/comfort-research/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/bin-there-dump-that/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/nothing-bundt-cakes/public"}],"shortDescription":null,"metaDescription":null,"altTexts":null,"jsonLd":null,"streamVideoId":"02b16450c3bad6077dbfe9d0de679463","roomCount":2}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('demetri', 'Demetri', 2012, 'completed', 0, 1, 1, '{"name":"Demetri","slug":"demetri","year":2012,"status":"completed","bio":"In early-November 2012, we were contacted by Children''s Healthcare of Atlanta about a special family who has had more than their share of challenges. Just three months earlier, fourteen-year-old Demetri was diagnosed with Stage IV Burketts Lymphoma.  His family had recently relocated from Florida to Atlanta to be closer to an ailing family member.   Living in unfurnished rental housing, there was real concern that Demetri, soon to be released from the hospital, would not have a bed to sleep in. Sunshine was there to help!  We immediately devised a plan to provide him a comfortable space to call his own. We learned that Demetri is a huge Miami Heat fan, so the theme of his bedroom was easy. Thanks to following companies; Fathead, Milliken rugs, Sports Coverage, Serta mattress, and Holland House furniture, for providing us the goodies we needed to sprinkle sunshine HEAT for Demetri to escape to!  In less than half an hour, 8 Sunshine volunteers arrived at Demetri''s house, assembled the bed and detailed it with new sheets, pillows, and comforter. We installed a huge Lebron James Fathead. At the informal reveal, the big smiles on the faces of Demetri, his mom and dad and two sisters informed us that we had fulfilled our mission. Demetri''s father tells us he hung out in his room the entire evening. ","quote":"In early-November 2012, we were contacted by Children''s Healthcare of Atlanta about a special family who has had more than their share of challenges. Just three months earlier, fourteen-year-old Demetri was diagnosed with Stage IV Burketts Lymphoma.  His family had recently relocated from Florida to","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/demetri/hero/public","roomTypes":[],"photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/demetri/hero/public","alt":"Demetri makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/demetri/photo-02/public","alt":"Demetri makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/demetri/photo-03/public","alt":"Demetri makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/demetri/photo-04/public","alt":"Demetri makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/demetri/photo-05/public","alt":"Demetri makeover photo"}],"age":null,"diagnosis":null,"_migration":{"cfHeroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/346d0a00-79f0-4c8b-c913-613048d8a600/full","source":"wix-migration","wixNumber":3},"roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('derek', 'Derek', 2016, 'completed', 0, 1, 1, '{"name":"Derek","slug":"derek","year":2016,"status":"completed","bio":"Derek Ivan Claros is a 16-year old who was born with Spina Bifida and Hydrocephalus. Spina Bifida is part of a group of birth defects called neural tube defects. The neural tube is the embryonic structure that eventually develops into the baby''s brain and spinal cord and the tissues that enclose them. Hydrocephalus is the buildup of fluid in the cavities (ventricles) deep within the brain. The excess fluid increases the size of the ventricles and puts pressure on the brain. Derek has been through 12 surgeries in his 16 years of life and the latest surgery for a shunt in his head required an extended stay for 40 days due to rejection. Derek uses crutches and a wheelchair on a daily basis interchangeably as he has no feeling in his lower extremities. Derek and his family reside in Norcross in Gwinnett County. Derek has a passion of sports and doesn''t let his disability deter him from excelling at his favorite sports. Derek has won medals in the Special Olympics and participates in Soccer, Hand Ball, Basketball and Swimming. Derek most recently played for the Gwinnett Heat Basketball team and in March 2016, his team advanced to the American Association of Adapted Sports Programs'' state championship game for wheelchair basketball.   Derek is a 10th grader at Meadow Creek High School in Gwinnett County and aspires to be a sports broadcaster when he grows up. His favorite Soccer team is Real Madrid and his favorite soccer athlete is Ronaldo. Derek''s life is powered by his belief to always trust the Lord and reach for his dreams. Overcoming many obstacles, Derek is a true inspiration to all.","quote":"Derek Ivan Claros is a 16-year old who was born with Spina Bifida and Hydrocephalus. Spina Bifida is part of a group of birth defects called neural tube defects. The neural tube is the embryonic structure that eventually develops into the baby''s brain and spinal cord and the tissues that enclose the","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/kalen/hero/public","roomTypes":[],"photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/kalen/hero/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/sofia/hero/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/sims/hero/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/andrew/photo-42/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/jack/hero/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/abby/photo-48/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/adrian/photo-30/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-08/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-09/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/ayden/photo-14/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/angel/photo-61/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-12/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-13/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-14/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-15/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-16/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/ayden/photo-20/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-18/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-19/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-20/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-21/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-22/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-23/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/derek/photo-24/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/briana-2016/photo-10/public","alt":"Derek makeover photo"}],"age":null,"diagnosis":null,"_migration":{"cfHeroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/bfce39e9-d0ab-4ba4-160b-dfe733fa9600/full","source":"wix-migration","wixNumber":42},"roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('desmond', 'Desmond', 2024, 'completed', 0, 1, 2, '{"name":"Desmond","slug":"desmond","age":7,"diagnosis":"Spina Bifida, Hydrocephalus, Club Foot, Bowel and Bladder Complications","roomTypes":["Accessible Bathroom","Dream Bedroom"],"year":2024,"status":"completed","bio":"Desmond has spina bifida, hydrocephalus and autism, but in no way do these diagnoses define him or limit his joy! His parents say is a social and caring person, always looking to greet anyone he meets in passing by shaking hands or giving a hug. Not only is he caring, but he is also fiercely independent and determined to do more things on his own; he knows what he wants! Because of this, he has always been structured in time scheduling and organization since birth. On any given day, you can find Desmond doing art, baking, cooking, out in nature, playing the piano or listening to music. He has such an imagination and loves being silly! Among his goals in life, he wants to be a veterinarian or as he calls it, a ''pet doctor.''\n\nThe makeover Desmond will be receiving will ensure that the space not only works for him now, but will continue to accommodate his needs for many years to come. Because of his diagnoses, he has no feeling below his knees. This requires him to use AFO braces. Getting into a bathtub or getting on hard flooring from his wheelchair is very careful work. Though he is independent and mobile with his wheelchair, they have to keep an eye on him as he can lose focus and be distracted in public settings due to his autism. Sunshine on a Ranney Day hopes to create a space for Desmond to feel safe and contained in his own bedroom, as well as a bathroom that gives space for increased independence and comfort.","quote":"\"He has such an imagination and loves being silly!\"","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/hero/public","photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-01/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-02/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-03/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-04/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-05/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-06/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-07/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-08/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-09/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-10/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-11/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-12/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-13/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-14/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-15/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-16/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-17/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-18/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-19/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-20/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/desmond/photo-21