cial/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/vicki-alsup/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/mohawk/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/rooms-to-go/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/randall-brothers/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/nugget/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/asv-productions/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/servicewise-electric/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/bin-there-dump-that/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/nothing-bundt-cakes/public"}],"shortDescription":null,"metaDescription":null,"altTexts":null,"jsonLd":null,"_migration":{"scrapedAt":"2026-03-06T13:32:09.487Z","source":"wordpress-xml-export","wpPostDate":"2022-12-08 21:43:58","wpCategories":["Meet the Kids","Reynard Custom Homes"],"wpTags":["2023","Accessible Bathroom"],"thumbnailId":5104,"needsReview":[],"cfHeroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/fc54d7c6-a12c-47ee-120d-cc03b0adc500/full"},"streamVideoId":"048b0ca08eb5edc4b987158a85b3f667","roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('hunter', 'Hunter', 2016, 'completed', 0, 1, 1, '{"name":"Hunter","slug":"hunter","year":2016,"status":"completed","bio":"Bright and adventurous is this handsome teenager, Hunter. He received an amazing dream room makeover and bathroom makeover from Sunshine on a Ranney Day. This 13-year old middle school student has never gotten less than an A and is in all advanced classes.  That is mighty impressive and admirable.  Hunter’s success is due to his dedication and ambition despite the challenges he faces. Hunter was born with an undiagnosed Central Nervous System Disorder. To this day, he does not have a confirmed medical diagnosis.  As an infant, he was not meeting expected milestones such as sitting up, rolling or pulling to stand.  He was referred to a neurologist and began physical and occupational therapy at 11 months of age. He has had multiple MRIs of the brain and spine as well as other extensive neurological assessments through the years, all of which show no identified abnormalities in the neurological structures.   After being examined by neurologists across the country, one thing they have all agreed upon is that Hunter presents like a Spinal Cord Injury. Unfortunately, the gold standard test to confirm this diagnosis is an Angiogram of the spinal cord, which would put Hunter at high risk for a stroke.  In order to protect him, this test is not going to be performed and an exact diagnosis is impossible.   A label is not required to keep this amazing young man thriving and enjoying this beautiful life!  Hunter perseveres with steadfast strength and continues to enjoy his favorite things such as playing Power Wheelchair Soccer with his travel soccer team, Sting, playing Minecraft, swimming, attending youth group and spending quality time with his family and friends.  He can often be found goofing off with his favorite pals including his 12-year old sister, Riley, his service dog, Osei, a toy poodle named Max, and a cat named Emily.   SOARD transformed his room and bathroom into an adventurous adobe where he can continue to bask in fun and shine, shine, shine, along with a wheelchair accessible bathroom where he can have as much independence as possible. ","quote":"Bright and adventurous is this handsome teenager, Hunter. He received an amazing dream room makeover and bathroom makeover from Sunshine on a Ranney Day. This 13-year old middle school student has never gotten less than an A and is in all advanced classes.  That is mighty impressive and admirable.  ","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/summit-counseling-center/hero/public","roomTypes":[],"photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/summit-counseling-center/hero/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/monica/hero/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/kalen/hero/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/jack/hero/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-05/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-06/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-07/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-08/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/angel/photo-61/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-10/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-11/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-12/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/hunter/photo-13/public","alt":"Hunter makeover photo"}],"age":null,"diagnosis":null,"_migration":{"cfHeroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/d02b92ba-53b9-4f96-fac7-00ebd2cdc000/full","source":"wix-migration","wixNumber":43},"roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('isra', 'Isra', 2017, 'completed', 0, 1, 1, '{"name":"Isra","slug":"isra","year":2017,"status":"completed","bio":"This mild mannered, adorable 11-year old is Isra.  Izzy is his nickname and he is the baby of the family. Izzy is a fun-loving little boy who loves Mickey Mouse Clubhouse, going to school, and a good therapy session. He receives physical, occupational, speech and vision therapies.   Izzy is very social and loves interaction.  He was diagnosed with Cerebral Palsy after a difficult birth when, for an extended time, he went without oxygen. The doctors didn’t believe that he would make it through the night, but he proved them wrong.  Eleven years later, Izzy is still fighting.  He has determined his own path and continues to climb that mountain every day. Izzy has extensive medical needs and it hasn’t always been an easy road.  He spent two long weeks in the NICU where he endured numerous medical evaluations, MRIs, blood tests, incubators and being on a ventilator.  When he came home, he suffered from seizures.  He is a quadriplegic and is fully dependent on others to meet his needs.  His entire family teams up to care for him, including his two adult siblings.  Although it is challenging, they consider it a blessing and Izzy has taught them a new degree of love.  His hugs, kisses, and countless smiles make it easy to treasure life’s simple pleasures as they watch him achieve his goals.    Izzy recently moved to a new home with plenty of green space.  He loves to feed the chickens and water the plants in the garden.  Since he has shared a room with his mom since birth and has a plethora of medical equipment, and his current bathroom is very small, Sunshine along with an awesome designer created a fabulous room tailored just for him and a bathroom he can get around in!  Sunshine on a Ranney Day knows these two rooms will bring him many more sunny days where he can bask in the glory of thriving in his very own dream room and wheelchair accessible bathroom. ","quote":"This mild mannered, adorable 11-year old is Isra.  Izzy is his nickname and he is the baby of the family. Izzy is a fun-loving little boy who loves Mickey Mouse Clubhouse, going to school, and a good therapy session. He receives physical, occupational, speech and vision therapies.   Izzy is very soc","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/isra/hero/public","roomTypes":[],"photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/isra/hero/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/christian-v/photo-29/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/andrew/photo-40/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/kalen/hero/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/amir/photo-33/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/grace/hero/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-21/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/isra/photo-08/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/sims/hero/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/bobby/hero/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/andrew/photo-42/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/anderson/photo-07/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/abby/photo-46/public","alt":"Isra makeover photo"},{"ur