/donors/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/gas-south/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/kids-r-kids/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/jackson-healthcare/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/chattahoochee-tech/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/rosalind-williams-photography/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/randall-brothers/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/real-floors-commercial/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/mohawk/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/sherwin-williams/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/lackey-drywall/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/echols/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/comfort-research/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/sunny-and-ranney/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/bin-there-dump-that/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/nothing-bundt-cakes/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/iframe-media/public"}],"shortDescription":null,"metaDescription":null,"altTexts":null,"jsonLd":null,"streamVideoId":"f34c5416772ac7d53e858c38912b026d","roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('pablo', 'Pablo', 2020, 'completed', 0, 1, 2, '{"name":"Pablo","slug":"pablo","age":13,"diagnosis":"Cerebral Palsy","roomTypes":["Accessible Bathroom","Dream Bedroom"],"year":2020,"status":"completed","bio":"At birth, he was diagnosed with cerebral palsy, diplegia, spasticity and asthma. Although devastated by this trauma, his family was determined to ensure that he had a brilliant future in which he''d achieve all of his goals.\n\nThis self-determined preteen is diligently working toward great achievements and does so with a happy spirit. He enjoys hippotherapy at MacKenna Farms where he has grown to love riding horses. He wears AFOs on his legs to help with tone and gait, as well as uses a wheelchair to get around on his own. He requires assistance with his activities of daily living including toileting and taking a shower. His home currently only has one bathroom and it is not wheelchair accessible. This makes his daily routine challenging and has become a barrier to developing further independence. Sunshine On A Ranney Day will be remodeling his bathroom to be fully accessible and will provide him an unforgettable designer bedroom. We can''t wait to see him beaming with glee when he sees it!\n\nPablo is fond of many things including dogs, classic cars, the color blue and Bruno Mars. Like most teens, he loves to chat about the things he loves most and those who know him best say he is quite the chatterbox. Despite the obstacles he faces, he continues to reach for the stars. \n\nWe hope that his newly decorated room inspires him to soar even further. We''d love to have your support in completing this project and hope that you will join us for the big reveal.","quote":"At birth, he was diagnosed with cerebral palsy, diplegia, spasticity and asthma. Although devastated by this trauma, his family was determined to ensure that he had a brilliant future in which he''d achieve all of his goals.","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/hero/public","photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-01/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-02/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-03/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-04/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-05/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-06/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-07/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-08/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-09/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-10/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-11/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-12/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-13/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-14/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-15/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-16/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-17/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-18/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/photo-19/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/pablo/ph