r-construction/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/signature-hardware/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/niki-murphy-photography/public"}],"shortDescription":null,"metaDescription":null,"altTexts":null,"jsonLd":null,"_migration":{"scrapedAt":"2026-03-06T13:32:09.470Z","source":"wordpress-xml-export","wpPostDate":"2021-06-26 22:39:44","wpCategories":["Crosby Design Group","Meet the Kids"],"wpTags":["2021","Accessible Bathroom"],"thumbnailId":1271,"needsReview":[],"cfHeroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/980e366f-9c04-44c1-de5b-1dc5652adb00/full"},"streamVideoId":"4ad80e2195a7ba9cf6b6d1ff12eb5811","roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('raynell', 'Raynell', 2021, 'completed', 0, 1, 1, '{"name":"Raynell","slug":"raynell","year":2021,"status":"completed","bio":"This strikingly handsome young man may look familiar to many of our Sunshine on a Ranney Day followers as he was one of the children we worked with in our early years. Raynel received our twenty-third designer room makeover. At the time, he was only nine.  He was delighted with his vibrant videogame themed room which was expanded to make room for his medical equipment and increase his ability to move around.  Now, Raynel is nearing his sixteenth birthday and has become an incredible young man.  Not only has Raynel grown quite a bit since his last makeover, but his family also had to move.  His current room and bathroom are too narrow to meet his needs for transferring, showering and moving throughout the home.  He is currently in need of a full adapted bathroom that will allow his chair to be rolled into the shower and decrease the physical strain of lifting him over the tub and supporting him during the bathing routine.\nRaynel has Spastic Quadriplegic Meningitis which was contracted at the age of four.  The effects of the infection led to many permanent disorders including obstructive hydrocephalus, cerebral palsy, a neurogenic bladder, developmental delay and hearing loss.  He is fully dependent for all activities of daily living.  Raynel has had a cochlear implant and is learning to use American Sign Language to communicate.  His parents are learning ASL along with him so that they can continue to communicate with him as his language advances. \nSunshine on a Ranney Day is ecstatic over being able to see how much Raynel has grown and continue to support him as his needs change.  He is truly extraordinary and continues to inspire us with his strength, positivity and illuminating smile.  We are eager to complete these renovations and see him smile once again!\n","quote":"This strikingly handsome young man may look familiar to many of our Sunshine on a Ranney Day followers as he was one of the children we worked with in our early years. Raynel received our twenty-third designer room makeover. At the time, he was only nine.  He was delighted with his vibrant videogame","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/summit-counseling-center/hero/public","roomTypes":[],"photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/summit-counseling-center/hero/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-18/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/bennett-and-lacey/photo-36/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/kalen/hero/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/amir/photo-33/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-21/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/sims/hero/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/zoe/hero/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-23/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/abby/photo-46/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/abby/photo-47/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-26/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-28/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-30/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/raynell/photo-15/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/raynell/photo-16/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-34/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/raynell/photo-18/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/raynell/photo-19/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/alejandro/photo-39/public","alt":"Raynell makeover photo"}],"age":null,"diagnosis":null,"_migration":{"cfHeroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/d02b92ba-53b9-4f96-fac7-00ebd2cdc000/full","source":"wix-migration","wixNumber":127},"roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('reese', 'Reese', 2022, 'completed', 0, 1, 1, '{"name":"Reese","slug":"reese","age":4,"diagnosis":"Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia","roomTypes":["Dream Bedroom"],"year":2022,"status":"completed","bio":"\"We weren''t the kind of parents who took our kids to the doctor for every little thing, but this was different.\"\n\nI sat alone feeling shattered into a million pieces, completely broken. Marcus walked in and I shared how our entire world had just been torn apart. We curled up next to Reese, holding him, caressing his cheeks, soaking the pillows with tears. I''ll never forget it. \n\nOne year later, and our sweet boy is in remission! Praise God! He''s continuing to receive chemotherapy and takes a revolutionary medication to turn off the Philadelphia chromosome; a rare chromosome he was diagnosed with in addition to Leukemia that essentially tells his body to keep making cancer.\n\nWe thought it would be super special for Reese and his older brother, Jett, to have a playroom where they can go to take their minds off the heaviness of this season we are in. Jett has had a very hard time as he''s often felt left out and forgotten. Sometimes he even says how he wishes he had cancer too. Reese adores Jett and this would give them a special area that is all theirs.","quote":"\"We weren''t the kind of parents who took our kids to the doctor for every little thing, but this was different.\"","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/hero/public","photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-01/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-02/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-03/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-04/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-05/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-06/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-07/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-08/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-09/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-10/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-11/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-12/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-13/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-14/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-15/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-16/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reese/photo-17/public","alt":""}],"photoCount":17,"videoUrl":"https://youtu.be/uScKoOHIJ-A","photographer":"Niki Murphy Photography","partnerLogos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/sunny-and-ranney/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/mohawk/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/real-floors-commercial/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/bin-there-dump-that/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/niki-murphy-photography/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/iframe-media/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/nothing-bundt-cakes/public"}],"shortDescription":null,"metaDescription":null,"altTexts":null,"jsonLd":null,"streamVideoId":"562cc6f712d467470a1d699019ca0f56","roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('reid', 'Reid', 2022, 'completed', 0, 1, 1, '{"name":"Reid","slug":"reid","age":7,"diagnosis":"Recessive Dystrophic Epidermolysis Bullosa","roomTypes":["Dream Bedroom"],"year":2022,"status":"completed","bio":"\"We are so pleased that Sunshine on a Ranney Day has offered to transform our bonus room into a dream bedroom for Reid.\"\n\nDespite living with this debilitating condition, Reid enjoys building with Lincoln Logs and riding his plasma bike. He also enjoys the company of his two older siblings, Avery and Barret. Although Reid has a feeding tube, he loves food! Even though eating can be painful, he enjoys small bites of cheese pizza and hotdogs when he doesn''t have any blisters in his mouth or throat. He is homeschooled and loves listening to Christian Hip Hop or watching The Spy Ninjas on YouTube.","quote":"\"We are so pleased that Sunshine on a Ranney Day has offered to transform our bonus room into a dream bedroom for Reid.\"","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/hero/public","photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-01/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-02/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-03/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-04/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-05/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-06/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-07/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-08/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-09/public","alt":""},{"url"