/imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-28/public","alt":"Reid makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-29/public","alt":"Reid makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-30/public","alt":"Reid makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/juana/photo-49/public","alt":"Reid makeover photo"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/reid/photo-32/public","alt":"Reid makeover photo"}],"photoCount":11,"videoUrl":"https://youtu.be/Emm8-2GNKJ8","photographer":"Pear Tree Photography","partnerLogos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/finlistics-2024/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/kids-r-kids/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/artisan-design-studio/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/reliable-heatingair/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/rooms-to-go/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/randall-brothers/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/five-star-painting/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/mohawk/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/wall-nut-custom-wall-murals/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/real-floors-commercial/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/pear-tree-photography/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/nothing-bundt-cakes/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/iframe-media/public"}],"shortDescription":null,"metaDescription":null,"altTexts":null,"jsonLd":null,"_migration":{"scrapedAt":"2026-03-06T13:32:09.474Z","source":"wordpress-xml-export","wpPostDate":"2022-01-24 21:03:00","wpCategories":["Meet the Kids","The Wall Nut"],"wpTags":["2022","Dream Bedroom"],"thumbnailId":4163,"needsReview":[],"cfHeroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/f6c61ccc-d2fc-45e4-a5ed-f927abd23500/full"},"streamVideoId":"5761822471fe541b91a053d02ce757a5","roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('remi-and-nico', 'Remi & Nico', 2026, 'in-progress', 0, 2, 1, '{"name":"Remi & Nico","slug":"remi-and-nico","age":14,"diagnosis":"Rare genetic disease","roomTypes":["Accessible Bathroom"],"year":2026,"status":"in-progress","bio":"Remi and Nico are two incredible sisters born with rare genetic mutations that have left them non-ambulatory and unable to communicate verbally. They rely entirely on their parents for daily care, yet they each express themselves in meaningful ways that those who know them understand and cherish.\n\nTheir parents, Tiffany and Patrick, have devoted their lives to caring for their daughters and remain steadfast advocates for their needs, both now and in the years ahead. As the girls grow into teenagers and young adults, their care needs continue to evolve.\n\nBoth Remi and Nico are tall, with beautiful long hair that requires careful attention. An accessible, thoughtfully designed bathroom is essential to allow Tiffany to safely and comfortably bathe them and care for their hair as they continue to grow.\n\nBecause his bedroom and bathroom are not wheelchair accessible, Axel is unable to move independently within those spaces. As a result, he must sleep in his parents'' room, separated from his twin brother, Angelo, something that limits both his independence and their ability to simply be kids together.\n\nDespite these challenges, Axel is a bright and spirited pre-teen. He loves to sing, spin joyfully in his wheelchair, which he skillfully controls with his head, and watch HGTV. (He''ll quickly tell you he has strong opinions about good design!)","quote":null,"heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/remi-and-nico/hero/public","photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/jackson/photo-01/public","alt":""}],"photoCount":1,"videoUrl":null,"photographer":null,"partnerLogos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/donors/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/kids-r-kids/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/real-floors-commercial/public"},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/partners/wyp/public"}],"shortDescription":null,"metaDescription":null,"altTexts":null,"jsonLd":null,"childCount":2,"roomCount":1}');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO kids (slug, name, year, status, featured, child_count, room_count, data) VALUES ('rheagan', 'Rheagan', 2021, 'completed', 0, 1, 2, '{"name":"Rheagan","slug":"rheagan","age":8,"diagnosis":"Spina Bifida","roomTypes":["Accessible Bathroom","Dream Bedroom"],"year":2021,"status":"completed","bio":"After numerous surgeries on her legs, and although she has no movement below the knee, Rheagan is able to use her wheelchair to get around independently\n\nWhen Rheagan gets home, her independence ends. Without an accessible sink, she cannot wash her own hands, and someone has to bring a cup of water to her for teeth brushing. While most kids her age have mastered an independent shower, Rheagan must be lifted into the tub and requires assistance to be safe. Like most girls, Rheagan wants to choose what to wear, but cannot reach her closet as her room is not accessible in many ways. \n\nAs Rheagan approaches her \"tween\" years, it would be fabulous if she had a safe, accessible space of her own to enjoy her favorite Star Wars, Disney Descendants, and Pok\\u00e9mon interests. The wheelchair doesn''t hold Rheagan back, and after a Sunshine on a Ranney Day room makeover, nothing will. Pinwheels are the perfect decor for her wheelchair!","quote":"After numerous surgeries on her legs, and although she has no movement below the knee, Rheagan is able to use her wheelchair to get around independently","heroImage":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/rheagan/hero/public","photos":[{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/rheagan/photo-01/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/rheagan/photo-02/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/rheagan/photo-03/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/rheagan/photo-04/public","alt":""},{"url":"https://imagedelivery.net/ROYFuPmfN2vPS6mt5sCkZQ/kids/rheagan/photo-05/public"